<table role="presentation" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td class="content">
      <h2>Account Access Removed</h2>
      <p>Hi <%= fullname %>,</p>
      <p>
        Your connection to <strong><%= companyName %></strong> on PropertyDesk has been removed as of <strong><%= disconnectedAt %></strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your role(s) — <strong><%= roles %></strong> — have been revoked and you no longer have access to this organisation's workspace.
      </p>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
        If you believe this was done in error, contact your account administrator directly. For further assistance, reach our support team at
        <a href="mailto:support@propertydesk.com">support@propertydesk.com</a>.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
